<title type="html"><![CDATA[Classic Shell 4.2.3 release candidate [Jul 26th, 2015]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4803&amp;p=20306#p20306"><![CDATA[
Here’s what’s new:<br /><br /><ul><li> Improved support for Windows 10</li><li> Improved support for touch keyboard</li><li> New command to access the PC settings directly (Windows 8.1 and Windows 10)</li><li> New settings to control the color and opacity of the Windows 10 taskbar</li><li> Multiple minor improvements and bugfixes</li></ul><br />You can download it from here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.mediafire.com/download/018hsjoas550hoh/ClassicShellSetup_4_2_3.exe">http://www.mediafire.com/download/018hs ... _4_2_3.exe</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Next release is <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4938" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.2.4</a><br />Previous release was <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4750" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.2.2 beta</a>.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sun Jul 26, 2015 9:31 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
